snippet.title: The Ancient Art of Staying Alive - new features (v1.2)
snippet.description:
Bombs away!

There are now obstacles to help (and maybe hinder) you, along with the ability to clear a small area around you, getting rid of both enemies and obstacles.

https://captaind.itch.io/the-ancient-art-of-staying-alive
